### 1. 商户审核售后（退货）
PUT http://localhost:8081/shops/1/aftersaleorders/1/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": true,
  "conclusion": "同意退货"
}

### 2. 商户审核售后（换货）
PUT http://localhost:8081/shops/1/aftersaleorders/2/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": true,
  "conclusion": "同意换货"
}

### 3. 商户审核售后（维修）- 会自动创建服务单
PUT http://localhost:8081/shops/1/aftersaleorders/3/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": true,
  "conclusion": "同意维修"
}

### 4. 商户审核售后（拒绝）
PUT http://localhost:8081/shops/1/aftersaleorders/1/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": false,
  "conclusion": "商品无质量问题，拒绝退货"
}

### 5. 商户取消售后（退货）
DELETE http://localhost:8081/shops/1/aftersaleorders/4/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": true,
  "reason": "客户要求取消"
}

### 6. 商户取消售后（换货）
DELETE http://localhost:8081/shops/1/aftersaleorders/5/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": true,
  "reason": "商品已经发出，无法换货"
}

### 7. 商户取消售后（维修）- 会同时取消服务单
DELETE http://localhost:8081/shops/1/aftersaleorders/6/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": true,
  "reason": "维修服务商无法提供服务"
}

### 8. 测试状态校验 - 只有待审核状态才能审核
PUT http://localhost:8081/shops/1/aftersaleorders/4/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": true,
  "conclusion": "测试"
}

### 9. 测试状态校验 - 只有已审核状态才能取消
DELETE http://localhost:8081/shops/1/aftersaleorders/1/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "confirm": true,
  "reason": "测试"
}

